                                                </div>
                                                <div class="button text-dark-1">What happens in case of bad weather?</div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="accordion__content">
                                                <div class="pt-20 pl-60">
                                                    <p class="text-15">In the event of bad weather, the safety of our participants is our top priority. Tour cancellations due to weather conditions are rare but may occur. If your tour is canceled, our customer support team will contact you to discuss rescheduling or refund options. Please check the tour details for specific weather-related policies.</p>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>


                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>
    </section>
